ck=\"gs(110003)\">1 Tim. 3:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110039\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110039)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110039)\">2 Tim. 1:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110071\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110071)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110071)\">2 Tim. 3:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">28. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109319\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109319)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109319)\">Rom. 8:39<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111802\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111802)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111802)\">Alma 5:44<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">29. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112756\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112756)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112756)\">4 Ne. 1:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">30. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111560\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111560)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111560)\">Mosiah 4:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112235\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112235)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112235)\">Alma 38:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">31. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112978\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112978)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112978)\">Moro. 8:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}